node.text:
#MERCEDESMONDAY
What better way to start the week than #MercedesMonday, especially in this gorgeous 1960 Mercedes-Benz 190SL!
You’ll surely capture all the attention in this highly desirable color combination of Fire Engine Red with a brown interior.
Key Features: 4-speed manual transmission, dual Solex carburetors, boot, steel wheels, white line tires, and Mercedes-Benz hub caps.
This is an extremely sought-after 190SL that has just come out of the dry desert state of Arizona and is available for $82,500
Please include your name, email, and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.

node.text:
A fun fact about one of the largest and most recognizable luxury car manufacturers in the world:
BMW was initially a manufacturer of airplane engines, and a good one at that. The company set records in aviation for both altitude and speed,
making key advancements in the industry before making the switch to the auto industry.
📷 Photographed yesterday at BHCC headquarters : 1973 Night Blue Metallic BMW 3.0CS with a sand beige interior.
Key Features: automatic transmission, power windows, headrest, wood steering wheel, power steering, and front-wheel disc brakes. A very
clean, highly collectible, and presentable E9 Coupe that is mechanically sound.
Now available at Beverly Hills Car Club for $59,950
Please include your name, email, and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.

Ferrari lovers, have you ever wondered where the name “400” came from?
#FerrariFacts
“Ferrari was already starting to stray from its traditional system at this point, but the 400 still has an old fashioned Ferrari name. That means the “400” in
the name comes from the V-12 engine’s unitary displacement, in other words, 400cc displacement per cylinder” -Top Speed
🤎 This amazing color combination 1979 Ferrari 400A is available in its factory color of Bruno Mogano with a sand beige interior.
Key Features: automatic transmission, air conditioning, power windows, power steering, and 4-wheel disc brakes. This is an excellent opportunity to jump
into the ownership of such an elegant Ferrari for $49,950
Please include your name, email, and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.
